  m_text: "HOW TO PLAY\r\n\r\nHold left click to charge your shot\r\nThe longer you
    hold, the stronger the throw\r\n\r\nWatch the wind direction \u2014 it affects
    your projectile\r\n\r\nDeal damage to your opponent's health\r\nFirst player
    to reach zero health loses\r\n\r\nGood luck!"
